content.rendered:
Directed by Bommarillu Baskar

Written by Bommarillu Baskar. Surendra Krishna

Star Akhil Akkineni (Harsha). Pooja Hegde (Vibha). Neha Shetty (Megha). Murli Sharma (Subbu). V. Jayaprakash (Harsha’s Father).ShivaKarthik . Vennela Kishore (Shoulder Shankar). Ajay (Harsha’s Brother-in-law). Aamani (Harsha’s Mother). Pragathi (Lokeshwari). Satya Krishnan (Harsha’s Sister). Manichandana (Ganesh’s Wife). Giri Babu (Judge). Krishna Murali Posani (Subbu’s Lawyer). Kasi Vishwanath (Defense Lawyer). Chaitanya Krishna (Vibha’s Ex). Amit Tiwari (Harsha’s Brother). Srikanth Iyengar (Ganesh). Ramesh Reddy (Harsha’s Uncle). Sudigali Sudheer (Sudheer). Getup Srinu (Sastry). Abhay Bethiganti (Harsha’s Friend). Eesha Rebba (Guest Appearance). Faria Abdullah (Guest Appearance). Rahul Ravindran (Vibha’s Cousin). Chinmayee Sripada (Vibha’s Cousin). Saanve Megghana (Harsha’s Prospective Bride). Aishwarya Hollakal (Harsha’s Prospective Bride).Sasha Singh . Kamakshi Bhaskarla (Harsha’s Friend). Mukhtar Khan (Megha’s Father).Anitha Nath

Language Telugu

Producers Guru Bobba. Satya Gamidi. Vasu Varma. Bunny Vasu

Production GA2 Pictures
